OL,3,CRSPCA 'at capacity' as large-scale
OL,4,Canimal rescues surge across the south
OL,6,FThe RSPCA is pleading for people to
OL,7,Fadopt animals in its care across the
OL,8,Fsouth after a surge in rescues where
OL,9,F10, 20 and even 100 pets were found
OL,10,Fkept at the same address.
OL,12,FLast year, more than 4000 rescues
OL,13,Facross the country involved at least
OL,14,Ften animals - with just under 400
OL,15,Fincidents in the south.
OL,17,FThe charity says it's regularly taking
OL,18,Fin animals kept in heart-breaking and
OL,19,Fcruel conditions.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
