PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1775311858
OL,3,CRSPCA 'at capacity' as large-scale
OL,4,Canimal rescues surge across the south
OL,6,FIn one recent incident, more than 250
OL,7,Fpoodle-cross dogs were rescued from
OL,8,Fthe same property. 87 of the dogs were
OL,9,Ftaken in by the charity while the rest
OL,10,Fwere signed over to the Dogs Trust.
OL,12,FAccording to the RSPCA, the living
OL,13,Fconditions and number of dogs had
OL,14,Fspiralled out of control due to
OL,15,Fextenuating family circumstances.
OL,17,FOther recent large-scale rescues
OL,18,Finclude an incident where 20 guinea
OL,19,Fpigs were signed over from a property
OL,20,Fin the South by an owner who was
OL,21,Fstruggling to cope.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
