OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1775311858
OL,3,CRSPCA 'at capacity' as large-scale
OL,4,Canimal rescues surge across the south
OL,6,FIn Dorset, the number of incidents
OL,7,Finvolving more than ten animals rose
OL,8,Ffrom 33 in 2024 to 53 last year.
OL,10,FThere was a similar rise in Wiltshire,
OL,11,Fwhich increased from 24 incidents to
OL,12,F40 across the same period.
OL,14,F"We are struggling with rising reports
OL,15,Fof cruelty and neglect and over recent
OL,16,Fyears more and more of those reports
OL,17,Fwill involve, 10, 20, even 100
OL,18,Fanimals," said Jo Hirst, RSPCA
OL,19,FSuperintendent.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
