FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1775311858
OL,3,CRSPCA 'at capacity' as large-scale
OL,4,Canimal rescues surge across the south
OL,6,F"And because they've been living in
OL,7,Flarge groups, they may need more
OL,8,Fsupport until they are ready to find a
OL,9,Fnew home."
OL,11,FShe added: "We currently have more
OL,12,Fanimals in our care than space in our
OL,13,Fcentres. These large animal rescues
OL,14,Fare adding to already overwhelmed
OL,15,Fanimal centres and local charities.
OL,17,F"We really need help from animal
OL,18,Flovers. If you are considering adding
OL,19,Fa pet to your home, please consider
OL,20,Frescuing. We need extra special homes
OL,21,Ffor some of our animals."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
