PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1775311858
OL,3,CRSPCA 'at capacity' as large-scale
OL,4,Canimal rescues surge across the south
OL,6,FAccording to Hirst, the growing number
OL,7,Fof rescues involving large numbers of
OL,8,Fanimals can be partially attributed to
OL,9,Fmental health issues and hoarding
OL,10,Famong owners. A comm
OL,12,FShe added: "Serious mental health
OL,13,Fissues and complex situations
OL,14,Finvolving animal hoarding are in part
OL,15,Fdriving these figures.
OL,17,F"It's vital that people are able to
OL,18,Fcontact us - or another animal charity
OL,19,F- where they have too many pets and
OL,20,Fare unable to cope."
